---
layout: base
description: "Ralph Hawkins is a service designer in the public sector, currently at NHS England. Weekly notes on the work of designing public services."
---
{# Get latest public weeknote (excludes preview posts) #}
{% set latestPost = collections.publicWeeknotes | reverse | first %}
{% if latestPost %}
<script>
  {# replace() keeps the homepage out of history so Back doesn't bounce
     the visitor forward into a redirect loop. #}
  window.location.replace("{{ latestPost.url }}?from=home");
</script>
<noscript>
  <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="0; url={{ latestPost.url }}?from=home">
</noscript>
<p>Redirecting to latest week note...</p>
<p>Click <a href="{{ latestPost.url }}"> if not redirected</a></p>
{% else %}
<p>No posts found</p>
{% endif %}
